ygData.messageBody:
It's correct tat the skull is found on gnoll embalmer, but the camp spawn
only gnoll during day and only undead (dry bone, greater mummy, lvl ard
24-25) during night.

On Tuesday, 03 August, 1999 12:33 PM, Alex [SMTP:leealex@...]
wrote:
> Skull of Jhen 'Tra can be found off the Gnoll embalmer at nite at Lake
rathne. It has a pet with it... ice skele , zombies and undead gnoll will
be around for the party. More stuff could be found of the embalmers,
sometimes. one time i got 4 items, skull (20 mana and 8sv), a stone,
Polished bone earring(10mana) and a weapon.
